  <!--
  Fields of the quotes

  quote.id      this must be set and match the used one in the filename
                e.g.: in 1000-abcde.en the 1000 defines the sorting order
                and abcde is the id; en then the localized version of
                the quote
  quote.image   may be set to the URL of the image of the person. The image
                should be squared
  name          the name of the person and maybe the profession
  text          the text of the quote
  read          if there is a longer interview text read should be set
  read.link     the URL of the interview text
  watch         if there is a interview video available watch should be set
  watch.link    the URL of the video
  -->

